casebody.data:
Abe LANGLOIS, Appellant, v. UNITED STATES of America, Appellee. No. 6451. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. May 1, 1931.

Before SAWTELLE, Circuit Judge, and KERRIGAN, District Judge.

PER CURIAM.

Pursuant to motion of appellee, ordered appeal in above cause dismissed for failure of appellant to file record and docket cause; mandate forthwith.
